Enkiguana naiguanareki Babilon


1   Tadou iyie totona te nterit na selenkei to e Babilon;

totona te nkop metii olorika le nkitoo,

naatito oo Lkaldayo! Amu meekure ae kata kingili aajo,

enasipa osesen naisikarra


2  Iwa lelo soito ooyutuutishoreki,

ndong'u entapa,

iwuang'ie ilo karasha limulumulare,

intayu ilo kila lino, ting'ishai too nkejek inono,

iima atua lkejek talang'a.


3  Kepuoi aaibalunye ina masipaisho ino,

nepuoi aadol enkurruna ino. Kaitalaku nanu elap,

nemaleku oltung'ani.


4  Ore Ilo okordu iyiook - naa Olaitoriani loo lororani,

ninye enkarna enye -

ninye Ilo Osinya le Israel.


5  Totona ntirring'ayu, nilo atua enaimin,

na tito oo Lkaldayo;

amu mikingili ae kata aajo

enkaiguanani oo nkitoriat


6  Atagorokine apa nanu iltung'ana laainei,

aisarkionie nanu enjung'ore ai;

aaishorua nanu apik atua nkaik inono,

neitu iyie ing'urrie ninche;

ore lelo moruak ntanapa iyie olola oiroishi oleng.


7  Itejo apa iyie, “Kaaku nanu enkaiguanani ntarasi,”

ore enkaraki ina eitu iyie ipik kuna baa atua oltau lino,

aashu idamu nkiting'ot enye.


8   Ore naa taata toning'o ena, iyie ena aisikarrani,

ena naton eidipakine,

ina najo to ltau lino,

“Atii nanu, nemetii ae neiijo nanu;

maton nanu anaa enkoliai

nemeye nkera aainei.”


9  Eikitum iyie kuna baa pokira,

te nkata nabo, te nkolong nabo;

ore keeya oo nkera inono o enkoliasho

naa eikitum iyie te nkiputakinoto hoo niata iloibonok kumok

o engolon kitok oo lasakutok.


10  Ndipakine apa iyie ti atua entorroni ino,

nijo, “maadolita nanu oltung'ani;’ ”

ore eng'eno ino o enkarriyiano ino nikintapong'oyie,

nijo iyie to ltau lino,

“Atii nanu, nemetii likae.”


11  Kake kelotu entorroni shumata iyie,

nemiindim iyie aibooi;

kelotu enkidaata shumata iyie,

nimindim iyie aitukuoi;

nelotu enkidaata enitii nabo kata,

neitu aekata idamu.


12  Ntasho tuunoyu ti atua esakutore ino

o lelo oibonok linono kumok,

laa ninche itanyamalikia ebaiki kitisho ino;

eidimayu pee imirisho,

eidimayu pee intureisho.


13  Inaure iyie te nena kiguanat inyi kumok,

nchoo naa ninche eitashe pee kintajeu,

lelo oor shumata,

ootoni aing'or ilakir,

laa ore te nedoli olapa neibonu ina nayooki alotu.


14  Ng'ura, eikununo ninche anaa suut,

neinos enkima ninche;

meidim ninche aaitajeu ate te ina golon o lng'ejep le nkima.

Mme inoshi kuk kuna naaiji,

neme enkima nanyikakinoyu!


15  neijia etiu te iyie ti alo nena baa apa nitanyamalikia,

laa ninche apa iyie imbung'are ti atua enkishui ino pooki;

kelo ake oltung'ani aim enkoitoi enye;

meetae hoo obo likilo aitajeu iyie.

